# Upgrade Application

### Step 1: Go to Upgrade Page
1. Log into your Admin Panel and navigate to the "Settings" section.
2. Click on the "Upgrade" tab.
[![image](/images/admin/settings/upgrade/1.png)](/images/admin/settings/upgrade/1.png)

### Step 2: Upgrade Application
1. Click on the "Upgrade" button.
[![image](/images/admin/settings/upgrade/2.png)](/images/admin/settings/upgrade/2.png)

2. Wait for the upgrade to complete.
3. Once the upgrade is complete, you will see a message that says "Upgrade Complete".
[![image](/images/admin/settings/upgrade/3.png)](/images/admin/settings/upgrade/3.png)